# Product Growth & Retention Dashboard

An interactive Tableau dashboard built using Kaggle e-commerce dataset.  
It tracks key product management KPIs:

1. "Customer Growth" (Active Customers per Month)  
2. Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR)  
3. ARPU (Average Revenue Per User) 
4. Churn Analysis (Active vs Churned Customers, 90-day rule)  
5. Top Customers Driving Revenue (Pareto/Segmentation)  

# Files
- 'Product_Growth_Retention_Dashboard.twbx' 
- data_cleaned.csv - Cleaned dataset with calculated metrics  

#Tools
- Tableau Public  
- Python (pandas, preprocessing)

